  "instructions": [
    "Heat sesame oil in a wok over medium heat until shimmering.",
    "Add cumin seeds and mustard seeds, stir until they start to pop for 30 seconds.",
    "Toss in diced carrot, celery, and onion, sauté until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add minced garlic and stir until fragrant, about 30 seconds.",
    "Gently fold in cubed tofu, cook until lightly browned on all sides, about 4 minutes.",
    "Drizzle soy sauce and rice vinegar over the mixture, stir to coat evenly.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 3 minutes to meld flavors.",
    "Meanwhile, warm the cooked rice in a separate bowl or microwave.",
    "Spoon the sautéed vegetables and tofu over the warm rice.",
    "Garnish with sliced green onions and a sprinkle of sesame seeds before serving."
  ],
